<section class="dms-band jumplink-section overflow-hidden pt-0 pb-lg-12" id="why-red-hat" data-analytics-region="why-red-hat"><div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-md-start align-items-xl-center justify-content-center pt-md-8 pt-lg-4 pt-xl-0">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-8 order-2 order-md-1 position-relative">
                <h2>Why Red Hat?</h2>
                <p>Red Hat is the world's leading provider of open source software solutions. <a href="/en/enterprise-open-source-report/2022?intcmp=701f20000012rEaAAI" title="The State of Enterprise Open Source 2022" data-analytics-text="In a recent survey" data-analytics-category="Why Red Hat?">In a recent survey</a>, 89% of industrial sector IT leaders believe that enterprise open source is as secure or more secure than proprietary software. Secure and innovative—those are benefits of working with communities—to collaborate to find the solutions to real-world problems, then harden for industries. <strong>This means:</strong></p>
                <pfe-tabs variant="earth" pfe-tab-history="" tab-align="center" class="mt-4"><pfe-tab role="heading" slot="tab"><h1>Open</h1>
                    </pfe-tab><pfe-tab-panel role="region" slot="panel" class="bg-gray-200 mt-2 mt-lg-4"><h2 class="text-center">Open hybrid cloud</h2>
                      <p>An <a href="/en/topics/cloud/open-hybrid-cloud-approach" title="Red Hat's approach to hybrid cloud" data-analytics-text="open hybrid cloud" data-analytics-category="Why Red Hat?|Open hybrid cloud">open hybrid cloud</a> strategy gives flexibility to run your applications across environments without having to rebuild applications, retrain people, or maintain disparate environments.</p>
                    </pfe-tab-panel><pfe-tab role="heading" slot="tab"><h1>IT/OT</h1>
                    </pfe-tab><pfe-tab-panel role="region" slot="panel" class="bg-gray-200 mt-2 mt-lg-4"><h2 class="text-center">Thousands of nodes</h2>
                      <p>The open hybrid <a href="/en/topics/cloud" title="Understanding cloud computing" data-analytics-text="cloud methodology" data-analytics-category="Why Red Hat?|Thousands of nodes">cloud methodology</a> allows IT and OT teams to maintain consistent control, visibility, and management of hundreds to thousands of edge nodes in an industrial environment.</p>
                    </pfe-tab-panel><pfe-tab role="heading" slot="tab"><h1>Edge</h1>
                      </pfe-tab><pfe-tab-panel role="region" slot="panel" class="bg-gray-200 mt-2 mt-lg-4"><h2 class="text-center">Enterprise edge experience</h2>
                        <p class="pr-2">The Red Hat <a href="/en/products/edge" title="Red Hat brings open source to the edge." data-analytics-text="portfolio of edge products" data-analytics-category="Why Red Hat?|Enterprise edge experience">portfolio of edge products</a> brings the familiarity of our open source platforms out of your datacenter to the devices at the edge of your network.</p>
                      </pfe-tab-panel><pfe-tab role="heading" slot="tab"><h1>Collaboration</h1>
                      </pfe-tab><pfe-tab-panel role="region" slot="panel" class="bg-gray-200 mt-2 mt-lg-4"><h2 class="text-center">Part of the community</h2>
                        <p>Through sitting on dozens of committee groups and <a href="/en/about/our-community-contributions" title="How we contribute" data-analytics-text="contributing to communities" data-analytics-category="Why Red Hat?|Part of the community">contributing to communities</a>, Red Hat is a driving force behind the transformation of manufacturing industries worldwide, steering toward more modern software practices.</p>
                    </pfe-tab-panel></pfe-tabs><img src="/rhdc/managed-files/tabs-pipe.png" alt="pipe" class="position-absolute d-none d-md-inline-block" id="tabs-pipe" /></div>
            <div class="col-lg-1 order-lg-2"></div>
            <div class="col-10 col-md-4 col-lg-3 order-1 order-md-3 mt-4 mb-4 mb-lg-0 d-flex justify-content-center">
                <img src="/rhdc/managed-files/man-computer.png" id="why-red-hat-graphic" alt="Illustration of a man with a laptop" /></div>
        </div>
    </div>
